#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:17
msgid ""
"CI runner on Python 3.10 reported ``solve_model returned False`` after a "
"409-second solve. The 4 x larger N-1 LP plus continuous-UC + piecewise-"
"heat-rate stack pushed HiGHS into a non-OPTIMAL termination status "
"(probably numerical, possibly tolerance-related) that wasn't reproducible"
" on the local conda environment. Killing N-1 in the regression scenario "
"shrinks the LP back to the v1.17 size and HiGHS solves cleanly."
