#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:258
msgid "PCM with ``prior_outflow`` (v1.17+): use the carried numeric."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:259
msgid ""
"PCM without ``prior_outflow`` (first window): drop the term -- the "
"v1.14.1 fallback, accurate only for the very first window."
