#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:402
msgid "Version 1.15.0 - May 6, 2026"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:404
msgid ""
"New feature: optional **unit commitment (UC)** overlay using a clustered "
"MILP formulation. Closes the LP-vs-PCM fidelity gap on the thermal-fleet "
"side: when enabled, each UC-eligible tech (typically coal, gas, oil, "
"biomass) is treated as a cluster of identical units of size "
"``tech_unit_size[te]``. The model now decides not just how much to "
"dispatch but how many units to start, run, and shut down each hour, with "
