"transmission. Layered on top of the existing transport-model "
"``trans_export`` variables -- the LP capacity bound stays in place; DC "
"flow adds Kirchhoff's voltage law via phase-angle differences. First step"
" toward production-cost-model fidelity."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/Changelog.rst:638
msgid "``prepshot/_model/dc_flow.py`` -- ``AddDCFlowConstraints`` class."
